data.title: Mitgliederprofil: Barbara Robinson Foreman – Find a Grave
data.meta_description: Die weltweit größte Grabsammlung. Beitragen, gestalten und entdecken Sie Gräber aus aller Welt. Mitgliederprofil: Barbara  Robinson Foreman – Find a Grave
data.text:
I started doing this when my mother past away in june 2014, I have allways found it interesting looking at old graves an wondering who they where an what were they like.Then it was like something in me said I had to do this give something back to those that have went before me, the ones forgotten, to me making a memorial for them lets people know this person was real. Now its a passion.

My family names are Robinson,Lewis,Ballard,Godwin.

My husbands are Foreman,Caldwell,Wright,Holyfield

Just to name a few

May God Bless each an everyone

Barbara
